loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="100"
data-flex-basis="242px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>そしてこの各ボタンにキーを割り当てていきます&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://blog.mikuta0407.net/posts/2021/20211207-making-wii-sensorbar-for-notepc/img/iMCrOrc.png"
width="370"
height="224"
